<section id="how-it-works" style="background:#faf1e3;padding:120px 32px">
  <div style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto">
    <div style="text-align:center;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto 56px">
      <div style="font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#bc7508;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.2px;margin-bottom:14px">How it works</div>
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-weight:700;font-size:40px;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin:0;color:#0a0a0a">The course lives inside your agent.</h2>
      <p style="font-size:17px;line-height:1.55;color:#737373;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:0">Not a video library. Not a PDF. A set of skills, instructions, and interactive components that turn Claude Code — or any capable agent — into the world's most patient tutor. Works with Codex, Cursor, Copilot, Open Code, and more.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px">

      <!-- Step 01: paste prompt -->
      <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding:28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-shadow:var(--os-shadow-card)">
