        <h3 style="font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-weight:700;font-size:22px;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin:12px 0 10px;color:#0a0a0a">Paste the install prompt</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.55;color:#737373;margin:0">Copy and pasting the prompt below drops the curriculum into your Claude Code (or any agent). The agent now knows every lesson, every checkpoint, every diagram.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:20px;padding:12px 14px;background:#111317;border-radius:8px;font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-size:12px;color:#d0d0d6;border:1px solid #f5e6c8;line-height:1.5;position:relative">
          <button
            data-copy={INSTALL_PROMPT}
            data-copied-label="✓ Copied"
            style="position:absolute;top:8px;right:8px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#d0d0d6;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;line-height:1.2"
          >Copy</button>
          <div style="padding-right:54px">{INSTALL_PROMPT}</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 02: build alongside -->
      <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding:28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-shadow:var(--os-shadow-card)">
        <div style="font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#bc7508;letter-spacing:1.5px">STEP 02</div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-weight:700;font-size:22px;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin:12px 0 10px;color:#0a0a0a">Build alongside your tutor</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.55;color:#737373;margin:0">Start a real full-stack app. The agent guides you module-by-module — explaining, pairing, and quizzing as you build real full-stack apps.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:20px;padding:12px 14px 14px;background:#111317;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #f5e6c8;font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-size:11.5px;line-height:1.6;color:#d0d0d6">
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:10px;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #2a2a30">
            <span style="width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#ff5f56"></span>
            <span style="width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#ffbd2e"></span>
            <span style="width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#27c93f"></span>
            <span style="font-size:10px;color:#7a7a82;margin-left:6px">~/my-todo-app</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px">
            <span style="width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:4px;background:#f5c518;color:#001a42;font-weight:800;font-size:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0">=&#125;</span>
            <span>Everything clear so far?</span>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:5px 8px;background:#2a2a2e;border-radius:3px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px">
            <span style="color:#7a7a82">&gt;&nbsp;</span>
            <span>Makes sense. Let's continue with the lesson<span style="display:inline-block;width:5px;height:11px;background:#d0d0d6;margin-left:2px;vertical-align:text-bottom;animation:ovBlink 1.1s steps(2) infinite"></span></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 03: interactive diagrams -->
      <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;padding:28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-shadow:var(--os-shadow-card)">
        <div style="font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#bc7508;letter-spacing:1.5px">STEP 03</div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-weight:700;font-size:22px;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin:12px 0 10px;color:#0a0a0a">Learn with interactive diagrams</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.55;color:#737373;margin:0">When concepts show up — request cycles, auth flows, DB operations — the agent renders a live diagram on top of your running app. Click, poke, understand.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:20px;padding:14px 14px 10px;background:#111317;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #f5e6c8;position:relative;overflow:hidden">
          <div style="position:absolute;top:8px;right:10px;font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:700;color:#f5c518;letter-spacing:1px">LIVE</div>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 280 84" style="width:100%;display:block">
            <rect x="6" y="22" width="56" height="38" rx="6" fill="#1c1c22" stroke="#34d399" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <text x="34" y="38" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--os-font-mono)" font-size="8.5" font-weight="700" fill="#34d399">BROWSER</text>
            <text x="34" y="50" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--os-font-mono)" font-size="7" fill="#7a7a82">React</text>
            <rect x="112" y="16" width="56" height="50" rx="6" fill="#1c1c22" stroke="#f5c518" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <text x="140" y="34" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--os-font-mono)" font-size="8.5" font-weight="700" fill="#f5c518">SERVER</text>
            <text x="140" y="46" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--os-font-mono)" font-size="7" fill="#7a7a82">Node.js</text>
            <text x="140" y="58" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--os-font-mono)" font-size="7" fill="#f5c518">/add-task</text>
            <ellipse cx="248" cy="34" rx="22" ry="6" fill="#1c1c22" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <path d="M226 34 V 54 a22 6 0 0 0 44 0 V 34" fill="#1c1c22" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <text x="248" y="50" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--os-font-mono)" font-size="8.5" font-weight="700" fill="#60a5fa">DB</text>
            <path d="M62 41 L 112 41" stroke="#f5c518" stroke-width="1.3" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="3 3" marker-end="url(#arrS)"/>
            <path d="M168 41 L 225 41" stroke="#60a5fa" stroke-width="1.3" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="3 3" marker-end="url(#arrD)"/>
            <text x="87" y="36" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--os-font-mono)" font-size="7.5" fill="#f5c518">POST</text>
            <text x="196" y="36" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--os-font-mono)" font-size="7.5" fill="#60a5fa">INSERT</text>
            <defs>
              <marker id="arrS" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="5" markerHeight="5" orient="auto"><path d="M0 0 L10 5 L0 10 z" fill="#f5c518"/></marker>
              <marker id="arrD" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="5" markerHeight="5" orient="auto"><path d="M0 0 L10 5 L0 10 z" fill="#60a5fa"/></marker>
            </defs>
          </svg>
          <div style="margin-top:6px;font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-size:10.5px;color:#a0a4ad;text-align:center">click any node → the agent explains it</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

