<section id="curriculum" style="max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:120px 32px">
  <div style="text-align:center;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto 56px">
    <div style="font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#bc7508;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.2px;margin-bottom:14px">Curriculum</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--os-font-mono);font-weight:700;font-size:40px;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin:0;color:#0a0a0a">Three phases, ship as you learn.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:17px;line-height:1.55;color:#737373;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:0">Each lesson is a set of skills your agent loads, a short reading, a running app, and a checkpoint you actually build. New modules drop as they're ready.</p>
